        | #[em Guidotti Riccardo, Monreale Anna, Ruggieri Salvatore, Turini Franco, Giannotti Fosca, Pedreschi Dino] (2022) - ACM Computing Surveys. In ACM computing surveys (CSUR), 51(5), 1-42.
